Even across the globe, there are very few personalities who parade such awesome credentials that Chief Obasanjo flaunts. The ex-president of Nigeria is undoubtedly favored by nature. At 85, he seems to have conquered his world. He appears to have achieved everything provident programmed for him so much that, even if the curtain is drawn on his existence today, there seems no outstanding chapter in his book of life remained to be opened.  Amzat is a Lagos based financial consultant. 